"  • your operating system, and hardware specs (CPU, RAM, GPU),\n"
"  • the Ansel version, and crash-free session statistics.\n"
"\n"
"We never send your images, file names, or any personal data.\n"
"\n"
"Data is collected by sentry.io and stored in Europe. You can review their "
"policy at https://sentry.io/privacy/.\n"
"\n"
